Package csc171.project02.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractAccount
    An abstract Account parent that defines and implements some Account state and behavior
    AbstractTransaction
    An Abstract Transaction parent object that defines and implements some state and behavior of Transactions
    AccountChecking
    This class is an empty child of the AbstractAccount, but it being distinct serves to clarify code in other locations.
    AccountSaving
    This Saving Account object inherits from the Abstract Account parent and provides additional Savings-specific state and behavior
    Bank
    The heart of the Model - all actions must go through the Bank.
    BankFactory
    A Factory for creating Bank objects populated with static template data.
    Customer
    A Customer Object that defines and implements the necessary state and behavior to define and uniquely identify a Customer to the Bank
    TransactionDeposit
    A Deposit Transaction Object
    TransactionWithdrawal
    A Withdrawal Transaction Object
    TransactionWithdrawalCheck
    A child of the Withdrawal Transaction @TransactionWithdrawal that provides specific Check behavior
    TransactionWithdrawalDebit
    A child of the Withdrawal Transaction @TransactionWithdrawal that provides Debit specific details
    Util
    This is a utility class for misc methods that don't quite fit anywhere else.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    TransactionWithdrawal.Type
    This enum lists the types of withdrawal possible
